特朗普正在推动立法者&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/zj_23iztHw6PfkuJpZJ1qXprKiD9lu5yrGyBHr1QVr3CV3QXCRIgmghvBNP29BvBJF_Rg2j1zJfYulYUgyNGC-HiN4nKqNtN4sGwdoG63mVsD5MBsktAnX2BoL_t3Zir206SbHJix-tee5mbso1hSDSS4jrhPQz5h1gzM3pehY86fx-nQ8qi5uqvxSiZprbqHiCm4JiytBRUES_y_XlS_rnrDNymZLr6ySDWqy8Ys7Xx-rjTwlHn9nb84QCR-2XWJPeule0BRqsmVCEGb8NOxIL7Og/P-FIKoTA9lEdOt7QrDmTuCUasukirR61/8" target="_blank" title="关联"&gt;对富人提高税收&lt;/a&gt;。熟悉讨论的人说，他呼吁为赚取至少250万美元的个人或赚取500万美元的夫妇提供新的39.6％的税率。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt; Panasonic计划裁员&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/zhbTya8g2XXmUeGRCJqxsDqNX9wOT7-5q337KCQAyjnJ0sKIGK-T8GNbKX2Tvo-4i_U5Z3T_hf-Tuf6vyBJDyQCC3mW1SgLGy0KINcB9vw77PJUkYa3pxp_to8YmkCJIcf2H7o0FToCeuQ4HlQONVImtWeV9NP79_-UQtGw8avFAwVFFqKxjRGiHCP26fRc3MGT8IgoiAJuk92LxFW3RfHt0DhNHUqsvQQKAfxaDcxmHCr-l2dvFMPsE0g24df0wZlV7mjBHf32YglelWDw5kbvu3w/dR6buFn7afJKMqia18eJHlenWKiTLjpG/8" target="_blank" title="关联"&gt;10,000个工作岗位，&lt;/a&gt;以此作为提高盈利能力的推动力。这家为特斯拉提供电池的日本公司旨在简化未生长的运营和修剪区域，例如工业设备和电视。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;em&gt;在&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/OEZPrlZL4Esn0hNZfjqTS1j0dah108X3-gpYFNhXDWJ8llCFiV7ykyXVFStFOC8IyVU9LXw-K8x0xNlbXqmCBQTOfg1hwsoIiiYvPA49r64wRXEs5N5w6O17fzhv7CbncV6hfYIt6aU0oV9CZNN8gjygNbxqsS4HN1ah_6f4xtairjUqeZAKjxe0qqfqRPYF4XXp93LY0V29Ry6UsENjLMGWeZsy_vaqgH3SmDen2yZo9kZ__0dTPeG-exZmOWHHlgR56JVA37anYAT7BmMiYHgOWg/dmeJJRMis8pFLl1YxwYuL0E2zHGOjtmj/8" target="_blank" title="关联"&gt;特朗普学&lt;/a&gt;的新情节中：尼尔·弗格森（Niall Ferguson）和菲德·扎卡里亚（Fareed Zakaria）加入了唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）在历史角度将唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）为美国经济的雄心勃勃的计划。在&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/h-eFfzGLFpIjbIqDiFMQ7hs1ps7NreZmi11epZu2HIn-wX1P5HtPCOnbFL2zkxHMyNMoHSqUtcOd2VX0vFWV40ja1wkK-fB0Xg3vujqiYyGqHAHjp-RWWfj_KkiqI3bTBGB0I2Wc-7FnNvDrJWTj5Hwxd8kbRnlfGPk7AYfr4Co1IqZcr5l6ZzNc6J4WcKzVgdBO_gdf4Iz22v3Dih5cOzJTYaXTezQKGuO1T2q269FM0bJ_PAyY-0a1f1SBhWIaSTj54KARXujbemYV6HLeaIRyEH1eHhyEUS